grid System / Flex :


1.what is css grid ?
	CSS grid is a 2 dimensional layout that helps you create Layout in both rows and columns

2. most important grid properties ?

	p1 - display : grid;  [allow in parrent][split data in grid types]
	p2 - grid-template-rows: ;  [allow in parrent][split data in row grid types]
	p3 - grid-template-columns: ;   [allow in parrent][split data in column grid types]
	p4 - grid: gap ;
	p5 - gap:
	p6 - justify-items : ;
	p7 - align-items : ;